apoorva ( kannada : apoorva &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 2016 indian kannada action film written and directed by v. ravichandran . the film stars v. ravichandran , apoorva &lt;unk&gt; , apoorva &lt;unk&gt; and apoorva &lt;unk&gt; in the lead roles . apoorva poonacha and apoorva dheer in the lead roles . apoorva poonacha composed the music for the film .